             (Police-constable C 42.) On the afternoon of the 10th of August I saw the prisoner in company with another; I went up, and followed them to <placeName id="t18320906-287-crimeloc1620">Vine-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18320906-287-crimeloc1620" type="placeName" value="Vine-street"></interp>
