                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-287-off1618 t18320906-287-crimeloc1620"></join>; the prisoner came back, stepped into the prosecutor's shop, and almost touched me as he came out; he stepped in again, and said, "Very well, Sir, I will tell him;" I thought I might be wrong in my suspicion - I looked into the shop, and there was no one there - I called to Stone, my brother officer, who took him with this valentia.</p>

